&lt;li&gt;Prepare production-ready files for digital and print projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain consistency across all brand touchpoints using established brand guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Website &amp;amp; SEO Support (30%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with updating website pages in Wix Studio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design graphics and layouts that improve user experience and engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help optimize webpages, images, metadata, and content for SEO best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support website maintenance by identifying outdated content, broken visuals, and opportunities for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
