&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Marketing team on product launches, fundraising campaigns, newsletters, and promotional materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resize and adapt creative assets for multiple channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with organizing design files, templates, and marketing resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct visual research and gather inspiration for upcoming projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Operations (10%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple projects simultaneously while meeting tight deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in design reviews and creative brainstorming sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate project updates proactively and seek feedback throughout the design process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously learn new tools, design trends, and marketing best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
