&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;sc-bcXHqe bTxoSk&quot;&gt;Grassroots Analytics (“GA”) is a political tech company dedicated to breaking down barriers in fundraising for progressive campaigns and causes. To facilitate that work, GA maintains a detailed database on more than 20 million active, left-leaning American donors, including data on net worth, ideological preferences, political donation history, non-profit donation history, demographics, and contact information. Our overall mission is to use that data to amplify forward-thinking voices, causes, and people.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grassroots Analytics is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team of experts and provide top-tier, individualized fundraising guidance directly to our clients. The &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; will collaborate closely with engineering to translate customer and market insight into SaaS products that help campaigns and nonprofit organizations run more effective fundraising operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone passionate about SaaS product strategy and data-driven decision-making, who thrives in a fast-paced, client-focused environment, and who&#39;s excited to help develop the next generation of product talent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Product Strategy &amp;amp; Roadmap Ownership (35%)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Director of Product &amp;amp; Research to align domain strategy with company-wide product goals. Define and lead product vision, strategy, and roadmap for an assigned product domain, translating market research and customer insight into compelling business cases and clear priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify new opportunities within the SaaS and DaaS landscape and build the business case for investment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal partners to drive end-to-end execution including GTM, Marketing, Data Science, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Cross-Functional Team Leadership (35%)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a cross-functional product team including UX Design and Engineering through the full product development lifecycle, from ideation through launch and iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and prioritize the backlog of epics, user stories, and supporting documentation, ensuring the team operates with clarity and shared purpose.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of accountability for on-time, high-quality hand-off of roadmap requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Customer &amp;amp; Stakeholder Advocacy (20%)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with UX to conduct customer interviews and synthesize qualitative and quantitative feedback to champion the voice of the customer throughout development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary liaison for the product domain across engineering, design, marketing, sales, and customer success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and monitor key product metrics, using data to evaluate feature success and inform iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mentorship &amp;amp; Team Development (10%)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and coach junior-to-mid-level Product Managers and other junior product team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to product team best practices, hiring, and onboarding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model the Grassroots Approach in all internal and external interactions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Grassroots Approach&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Grassroots Analytics, our work is guided by the following principle
